responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "8B11408E426C704EE81B2685B36B59EB", "While perusing the local market for recovered trinkets I happened upon a tattered journal that belonged to my great grandfather, Roderic. My delight became demise as not only was I forced to pay heavy glint for it, but I discovered the most important pages removed. No doubt they are scattered amidst the madness that has overtaken the estate.")
